      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>When you use your action to @action[Dash], you can use a bonus action to make one melee weapon attack or to @action[shove] a creature.</p><p>If you move at least 10 feet in a straight line immediately before taking this bonus action, you either gain a +5 bonus to the attack's damage roll (if you chose to make a melee attack and hit) or push the target up to 10 feet away from you (if you chose to shove and you succeed).</p></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
